            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EEzekiel%2035%3A1-36%3A38%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_35_1%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EEzekiel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E35%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EA%20Message%20for%20Edom%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EAgain%20a%20message%20came%20to%20me%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3A%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_35_2%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSon%20of%20man%2C%20turn%20and%20face%20Mount%20Seir%2C%20and%20prophesy%20against%20its%20people.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_35_3%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EGive%20them%20this%20message%20from%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20am%20your%20enemy%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3BMount%20Seir%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20I%20will%20raise%20my%20fist%20against%20you%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eto%20destroy%20you%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_35_4%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20demolish%20your%20cities%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20make%20you%20desolate.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThen%20you%20will%20know%20that%20I%20am%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_35_5%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BYour%20eternal%20hatred%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20led%20you%20to%20butcher%20them%20when%20they%20were%20helpless%2C%20when%20I%20had%20already%20punished%20them%20for%20all%20their%20sins.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_35_6%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EAs%20surely%20as%20I%20live%2C%20says%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20since%20you%20show%20no%20distaste%20for%20blood%2C%20I%20will%20give%20you%20a%20bloodbath%20of%20your%20own.%20Your%20turn%20has%20come!%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_35_7%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20make%20Mount%20Seir%20utterly%20desolate%2C%20killing%20off%20all%20who%20try%20to%20escape%20and%20any%20who%20return.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_35_8%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20fill%20your%20mountains%20with%20the%20dead.%20Your%20hills%2C%20your%20valleys%2C%20and%20your%20ravines%20will%20be%20filled%20with%20people%20slaughtered%20by%20the%20sword.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_35_9%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20make%20you%20desolate%20forever.%20Your%20cities%20will%20never%20be%20rebuilt.%20Then%20you%20will%20know%20that%20I%20am%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_35_10%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BFor%20you%20said%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BThe%20lands%20of%20Israel%20and%20Judah%20will%20be%20ours.%20We%20will%20take%20possession%20of%20them.%20What%20do%20we%20care%20that%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20there!%26%23x2019%3B%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_35_11%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3ETherefore%2C%20as%20surely%20as%20I%20live%2C%20says%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20I%20will%20pay%20back%20your%20angry%20deeds%20with%20my%20own.%20I%20will%20punish%20you%20for%20all%20your%20acts%20of%20anger%2C%20envy%2C%20and%20hatred.%20And%20I%20will%20make%20myself%20known%20to%20Israel%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E35%3A11%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eto%20them%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20Greek%20version%20reads%20%3Cem%3Eto%20you.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20by%20what%20I%20do%20to%20you.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_35_12%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20you%20will%20know%20that%20I%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20have%20heard%20every%20contemptuous%20word%20you%20spoke%20against%20the%20mountains%20of%20Israel.%20For%20you%20said%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BThey%20are%20desolate%3B%20they%20have%20been%20given%20to%20us%20as%20food%20to%20eat!%26%23x2019%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_35_13%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20saying%20that%2C%20you%20boasted%20proudly%20against%20me%2C%20and%20I%20have%20heard%20it%20all!%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_35_14%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20The%20whole%20world%20will%20rejoice%20when%20I%20make%20you%20desolate.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_35_15%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20rejoiced%20at%20the%20desolation%20of%20Israel%26%23x2019%3Bs%20territory.%20Now%20I%20will%20rejoice%20at%20yours!%20You%20will%20be%20wiped%20out%2C%20you%20people%20of%20Mount%20Seir%20and%20all%20who%20live%20in%20Edom!%20Then%20you%20will%20know%20that%20I%20am%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_36_1%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EEzekiel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E36%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3ERestoration%20for%20Israel%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSon%20of%20man%2C%20prophesy%20to%20Israel%26%23x2019%3Bs%20mountains.%20Give%20them%20this%20message%3A%20O%26%23xA0%3Bmountains%20of%20Israel%2C%20hear%20the%20word%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E!%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_36_2%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20is%20what%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20Your%20enemies%20have%20taunted%20you%2C%20saying%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BAha!%20Now%20the%20ancient%20heights%20belong%20to%20us!%26%23x2019%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_36_3%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ETherefore%2C%20son%20of%20man%2C%20give%20the%20mountains%20of%20Israel%20this%20message%20from%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3A%20Your%20enemies%20have%20attacked%20you%20from%20all%20directions%2C%20making%20you%20the%20property%20of%20many%20nations%20and%20the%20object%20of%20much%20mocking%20and%20slander.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_36_4%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3ETherefore%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3Bmountains%20of%20Israel%2C%20hear%20the%20word%20of%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20He%20speaks%20to%20the%20hills%20and%20mountains%2C%20ravines%20and%20valleys%2C%20and%20to%20ruined%20wastes%20and%20long-deserted%20cities%20that%20have%20been%20destroyed%20and%20mocked%20by%20the%20surrounding%20nations.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_36_5%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20is%20what%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20My%20jealous%20anger%20burns%20against%20these%20nations%2C%20especially%20Edom%2C%20because%20they%20have%20shown%20utter%20contempt%20for%20me%20by%20gleefully%20taking%20my%20land%20for%20themselves%20as%20plunder.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_36_6%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BTherefore%2C%20prophesy%20to%20the%20hills%20and%20mountains%2C%20the%20ravines%20and%20valleys%20of%20Israel.%20This%20is%20what%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20I%20am%20furious%20that%20you%20have%20suffered%20shame%20before%20the%20surrounding%20nations.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_36_7%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3ETherefore%2C%20this%20is%20what%20the%20Sovereign%20